      <title>饮酒者减少支出导致帝亚吉欧受拉丁美洲市场衰退影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/diageo-hit-by-latin-america-slump-as-drinkers-rein-in-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲、加勒比地区和美国经济的放缓导致英国酿酒商帝亚吉欧 (Diageo Plc) 的年度销售额自疫情爆发以来首次下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/diageo-hit-by-latin-america-slump-as-drinkers-rein-in-spending</guid>
